&nbsp;&nbsp;opposed by the defender's Dexterity or Strength check (whichever ability score has the higher modifier&#41;:
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;[PC](!&#13;Dexterity or Strength check for &amp;commat;{selected|character_name}:
&amp;lsqb;&amp;lsqb; 1d20 + &amp;lsqb;&amp;lsqb; {&amp;commat;{selected|str-mod},&amp;commat;{selected|dex-mod} }kh1&amp;rsqb;&amp;rsqb; &amp;rsqb;&amp;rsqb;&#41; [NPC](!&#13;Dexterity or Strength check for &amp;commat;{selected|character_name}:
