}&#125; )
[Sunder](!&#13;
&amp;{template:DnD35StdRoll} {{pcflag=true}&#125; {{name=&#42;&#42;[Sunder](https://www.dandwiki.com/wiki/SRD:Sunder&#41;&#42;&#42;}&#125; {{subtags=@{selected|character_name}&#125;} {{check=&#42;&#42;Sunder check:&#42;&#42;}&#125; {{Opposing check=&#42;&#42;Melee Weapon Attack&#42;&#42;}&#125; {{Duration=1 Std Action}&#125; {{Provoke Attack of Opp=Yes}&#125; {{checkroll=&#42;&#42;Melee Weapon Attack&#42;&#42;}&#125; {{notes=
