Step Two: (Opposed Rolls&#41;
• Two-Handed weapons gain &grave;&grave;+4&grave;&grave; bonus.
• Light weapons take a &grave;&grave;-4&grave;&grave; penalty.
• If combatants differ in sizes, larger gains &grave;&grave;+4&grave;&grave; per size category.

Step Three: (Consequences&#41;
• If you beat the defender, roll damage and deal it using information from [this table](https://www.dandwiki.com/wiki/SRD:Sunder&#41;.}&#125; )
